        <p class="large-text">Unlike natural marble installations that require grout lines and ongoing maintenance, our metallic marble systems provide the timeless elegance of Italian marble with enhanced performance characteristics. Each installation features custom veining, metallic accents, and pearlescent finishes that capture the depth and luminosity of natural stone.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>

  <!-- Differentiators Section -->
  <Container>
    <section class="differentiators-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Technical Excellence in Marble Reproduction</h2>
        <p>Our metallic marble systems deliver superior performance through specialized application techniques and premium materials:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Multi-Coat Metallic Application Process</h3>
          <p>Specialized layering technique using premium metallic stains and accent materials to achieve authentic marble depth and veining patterns</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Custom Color Matching Capabilities</h3>
          <p>Precise color formulation and matching to specific marble varieties, architectural elements, or custom design specifications</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Durability Superior to Natural Marble</h3>
          <p>Enhanced resistance to staining, etching, and wear while maintaining the aesthetic beauty of authentic Italian marble</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Seamless Installation Advantage</h3>
          <p>Eliminates grout lines and seams that plague natural marble tile installations, creating uninterrupted marble surfaces</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Italian Marble Reproduction Specialty</h3>
          <p>Expert recreation of Carrara, Calacatta, Statuario, and other premium Italian marble varieties with metallic enhancement</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <Container>
    <section class="process-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Professional Metallic Epoxy Installation Process</h2>
        <p>Our metallic epoxy installation process combines technical expertise with artistic craftsmanship for optimal results:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-number">1</div>
          <h3>Surface Preparation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Testing for previous applications and contamination</li>
            <li>Diamond grinding with 25 grit metal diamonds</li>
            <li>Joint and crack filling and repair</li>
            <li>Thorough cleaning for optimal adhesion</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-number">2</div>
          <h3>Base Coat Application</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Dark solid color base coat to enhance metallic effect</li>
            <li>Uniform coverage with professional equipment</li>
            <li>Surface preparation for metallic layer</li>
            <li>Quality control and timing management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-number">3</div>
          <h3>Metallic Layer Installation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Premium metallic flakes and pigments application</li>
            <li>Continuous incorporation during curing process</li>
            <li>Pattern development and movement creation</li>
            <li>Working within optimal timing window</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card">
