            <li>Specialized solvents and blowers for effects</li>
            <li>Creating lava, wave, or cloud patterns</li>
            <li>Real-time artistic adjustments and refinement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-number">5</div>
          <h3>Protective Finish</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Clear topcoat for surface protection</li>
            <li>UV-stable formulation for color retention</li>
            <li>Seamless waterproof seal completion</li>
            <li>Final inspection and quality assurance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>

  <!-- Collections Section -->
  <Container>
    <section class="collections-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Premium Metallic Marble Product Line</h2>
        <p>Choose from our specialized marble systems, each designed to create authentic luxury marble finishes:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="collections-grid">
        <div class="collection-card">
          <a href="/services/metallic-marble-stains" class="collection-link">
            <h3>Metallic Marble Stains</h3>
            <p class="collection-desc">Our signature specialty for premium marble reproduction</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Proprietary metallic stain formulations</li>
              <li>Multi-layer application for depth and authenticity</li>
              <li>Superior color retention and durability</li>
              <li>Custom blend capabilities for unique finishes</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="learn-more">Learn More →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="collection-card">
          <a href="/services/italian-marble-reproduction" class="collection-link">
            <h3>Italian Marble Reproduction</h3>
            <p class="collection-desc">Premium positioning with authentic Italian marble patterns</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Carrara, Calacatta, and Statuario reproductions</li>
              <li>Precise veining pattern replication</li>
              <li>Luxury positioning for high-end projects</li>
              <li>Historical Italian marble authenticity</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="learn-more">Learn More →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="collection-card">
          <a href="/services/veined-marble-effects" class="collection-link">
            <h3>Veined Marble Effects</h3>
            <p class="collection-desc">Dramatic veining patterns enhanced with metallic accents</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Bold, flowing veining patterns</li>
              <li>Metallic accent integration throughout veins</li>
              <li>High-contrast dramatic marble effects</li>
              <li>Perfect for statement walls and feature areas</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="learn-more">Learn More →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="collection-card">
          <a href="/services/pearlescent-marble-finishes" class="collection-link">
            <h3>Pearlescent Marble Finishes</h3>
            <p class="collection-desc">Sophisticated pearl-like luminosity with marble patterns</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Subtle pearlescent shimmer effects</li>
              <li>Elegant luminosity that changes with lighting</li>
              <li>Sophisticated marble patterns with pearl enhancement</li>
              <li>Perfect for luxury residential and hospitality</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="learn-more">Learn More →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="collection-card">
          <a href="/services/custom-color-metallic-systems" class="collection-link">
            <h3>Custom Color Metallic Systems</h3>
            <p class="collection-desc">Completely personalized marble systems with custom colors</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Unlimited custom color combinations</li>
              <li>Brand color integration capabilities</li>
              <li>Architectural color matching services</li>
              <li>One-of-a-kind marble systems tailored to vision</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="learn-more">Learn More →</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>


  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="contact-section">
    <Container>
      <div class="contact-content">
        <div class="contact-info">
          <h2>Ready to Transform Your Space?</h2>
          <p>Schedule your premium design consultation today and discover how our metallic marble systems can transform your space into a work of art.</p>
          
          <div class="contact-methods">
            <div class="contact-button-wrapper">
              <p class="contact-label">Call</p>
              <a href="tel:+15132965525" class="contact-button contact-button-phone">
                <div class="contact-details">
                  <span class="contact-info">(513) 296-5525</span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="contact-button-wrapper">
              <p class="contact-label">Email</p>
              <a href="mailto:john@queencitysurfacecoatings.com" class="contact-button contact-button-email">
                <div class="contact-details">
                  <span class="contact-info">john@queencitysurfacecoatings.com</span>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-form">
          <QuoteRequestForm />
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
